      "title": "Compliance with IMF: Prime Minister",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena announced in Parliament today (01) that an agreement has been reached at the official level to obtain a four-year extended credit facility of $2.9 billion from the International Monetary Fund."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
        [
          {
